A kivy-based app for helping keep track of VTES games.

Basic UI is:

   Setup game details
      Player names, in bleed order
        (Space for deck type notes)

   advance turns
      Each turn has space for notes
         Useful shortcuts
            - Play master
            - Bring out minion (space for name)
            - Minion X Bleeds
            - Minion X calls a votes
            - Minion X takes other action
            - Minion Y blocks
            - Combat
            - Minion X goes to torpor

   Note ousting:
      - Will skip ousted players thereafter
